  "reference_number": "RUS1648",
  "remarks": "\nKonstantin IVASHCHENKO is the Russian appointed head of the Mariupol city administration, following Russian forces’ occupation of Mariupol. IVASHCHENKO is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because in this role he supports and promotes actions and policies that destabilise and undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty, or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
